{"tid":2218301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽聞有一大耳賊劉備想阻我曹魏統一霸業","createTime":"2020-09-26T06:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T15:54:35.000Z","uid":229502,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fd01e366968715d83192307bb49791fddfe62d5a","tid":2218301,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:17:48.000Z","msg":"備會操於營中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 劉備 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:曹操<br />\n<br />\n操曰：「天下之大，何物為貴？」<br />\n備曰：「一為妻，二為子，三為兄弟。」<br />\n操曰：「妻，子，兄弟，何物為貴？。」<br />\n備曰：「兄弟如手足，妻子如衣服。」<br />\n操曰：「好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><em>(以上故事純粹虛構)</em></span><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------<br />\n手足，呢個詞，小弟我認為嘅意思係「將同路人擺喺比親人更重要嘅位置所作嘅稱呼」，可能呢個詞真正嘅意思唔係咁，但自問我哋有幾多個人可以做得差唔到嘅嘢？我認為流亡海外之後仲幫我哋作戰嘅同路人係手足，不顧一切想打倒政權嘅人係手足，但你諗下自己係咪不顧一切，拋棄親人移民之後都會幫我哋作戰？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong>我撫心自問做唔到，所以我唔會要求大家咁嚴格，不過我哋可以慢慢做起<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>1.由生活做起</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">買嘢嗰陣睇下係咪中国貨，係咪黃店，黃店唔係淨係得食嘢，阿布泰之類唔同種類嘅店舖都係黃店</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">搭車盡量用散銀，搭的士可以搭黃的，搭黨鐵就盡量唔好搭，如果真係要搭就眼觀四面，留意周圍有冇可疑人物先好搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">多啲向身邊嘅人分享關於運動嘅情況，唔好畀佢冷淡落嚟，對住街坊有機會可以潛移默化咁向佢灌輸黃色嘅意識</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong>2.由平時做嘅嘢做起<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"red\">每日抽啲時間打國際線，例如Twitter，Reddit等，同喺TVB戰線畀嬲。當你想碌FB，IG嗰陣，提醒自己打咗國際線，TVB戰線，同埋其他可以幫忙嘅戰線</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\">每日做下運動，就算做唔到都要畀身體郁下，養兵千日用在一時，你唔知幾時會用到呢副身體，但都唔好過勞，要適當</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong>3.由心態做起</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">提醒自己仲未完，未輸，未贏，所以要做多啲嘢去贏，就算感到無力都好，你做到嘢已經得，之後愈做愈多。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">以勸喻取代批評，以思考取代抗拒，見到有人做得唔好屌人，要用提議嘅方式。見到有人話你做得唔好，唔好即刻話人有異心，要諗下自己係咪真係有問題。互屌只會踏入惡性循環</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">唔好放fake news，fake news只會令我哋錯判形勢。唔好自high，人喺亢奮嘅時候係好可以忘我。唔好亂捉毛，當自己人都信唔過自己人嘅時候，士氣會不振，除非你100%肯定嗰個人係五毛，就可以提醒其他人，唔好畀機會佢擾亂軍心</span><br />\n<br />\n如果你問我做呢啲嘢係咪就可以叫同路人做手足，唔好。但係你做晒就會明我嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，劉備講「兄弟如手足，妻子如衣服。」係出自三國演義，佢係咪真係講過呢句嘢就唔知喇，不過大家都要有覺悟為大家付出更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092825b6d185f04d5bb343e023f4065afd2c9cad","tid":2218301,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493f20bb6daeed2150d3954703ba668f07e43378","tid":2218301,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c32a78316c4b22f3b029d653915c84f458995e","tid":2218301,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1520eb946c4eae1951f6dce0f36dc6b828c7d3db","tid":2218301,"uid":266294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd55535780db1746ead3d71ca99525a070cec4d","tid":2218301,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a550778b894b2fd0d86f3ceb1a1b7fe06368fd","tid":2218301,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1520eb946c4eae1951f6dce0f36dc6b828c7d3db","tid":2218301,"uid":266294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97971aca7ef7be449e6e3b8cf756bf97084ed787","tid":2218301,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img s