e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:22:57.000Z","msg":"抗爭由生活做起講咗成年<br />\n都未開始做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f9eba665417098bfcebdb7d1f57d5269be74b8","tid":2218301,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"925a174dea205cc5f26e1344c9b0915fa2d291cf","tid":2218301,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:28:08.000Z","msg":"推依個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋係手足.....手足。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2218320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2218320</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}}